             was indicted for <rs id="t18150510-66-off399" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18150510-66-off399" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150510-66-off399" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18150510-66-cd400" type="crimeDate">29th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150510-66-off399 t18150510-66-cd400"></join>, a watch, value 2 l. 2 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18150510-66-victim675" type="victimName">
                           Joseph 
                           Hardy
                        <interp inst="t18150510-66-victim675" type="surname" value="Hardy"></interp>
